│ removing the ninf flag from maxnum/minnum intrinsics, which changes the     │
│ fast math flags from "fast" to individual flags like "reassoc nnan nsz arcp │
│ contract afn". This is the correct behavior because the ninf flag should    │
│ not be applied to maxnum/minnum intrinsics.                                 │
│                                                                             │
